^I^I^I&nbsp;









LOOPZ




^Ilabel





Decrease CX, jump to label if CX not zero and ZF = 1. Algorithm:



CX = CX - 1
if (CX &lt;> 0) and (ZF = 1) then
^I
^Ijump
^I
^Ielse
^I
^Ino jump, continue
^I



^I
^Iexample for emu8086 emulator:

; Loop until result fits into AL alone,
; or 5 times. The result will be over 255
; on third loop (100+100+100),
; so loop will exit.
   include 'emu8086.inc'
   ORG 100h
   MOV AX, 0
   MOV CX, 5
label1:
   PUTC '*'
   ADD AX, 100
   CMP AH, 0
   LOOPZ label1
   RET



